8
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:19,815
<font color="#ffff00">Watchers : Para Penjaga</font>

9
00:01:29,322 --> 00:01:30,892
<font color="#ffff00">Para Penjaga membantu keturunan Cain...</font>

10
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:33,163
