<font color="#ffff00">Putraku.</font>

21
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:40,646
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta menciptakan
Adam atas kehendak-Nya...,</font>

22
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:43,564
<font color="#ffff00">...dan memasrahkan dunia padanya.</font>

23
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:48,410
<font color="#ffff00">Ini tugasmu sekarang.
Tanggung jawabmu.</font>

24
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:55,529
<font color="#ffff00">Semoga kau berjalan di sisi
Sang Pencipta dalam kebajikan.</font>

25
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,523
<font color="#ffff00">Kuperintahkan padamu...</font>

26
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,051
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tempat suci Seth !</i></font>

27
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,168
<font color="#ffff00">Ada orang.</font>

28
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,810
<font color="#ffff00">Sembunyi.</font>

29
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,608
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kita menambang di sini.</i></font>

30
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,690
<font color="#ffff00">Tanahnya kaya akan tzohar.</font>

31
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:29,488
<font color="#ffff00">Ini tanah Sang Pencipta.
Apa yang kau lakukan ?</font>

32
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,884
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta ?</font>

33
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,128
<font color="#ffff00">Tambangku mulai habis.</font>

34
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:38,010
<font color="#ffff00">Rakyatku lemah dan
harus diberi makan.</font>

35
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:41,129
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu apa yang Dia lakukan ?</font>

36
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:45,649
<font color="#ffff00">Dia mengutuk kita untuk berusaha
dengan keringat agar bertahan hidup !</font>

37
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:49,805
<font color="#ffff00">Terkutuk aku jika aku
hanya diam saja.</font>

38
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:55,323
<font color="#ffff00">Terkutuk aku jika tak mengambil
apapun yang kuinginkan.</font>

39
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:07,283
<font color="#ffff00">Peninggalan ini jadi milik
keturunan Cain sekarang.</font>

40
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,162
<font color="#ffff00">Garis keturunan Seth berakhir di sini.</font>

41
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:20,008
<font color="#ffff00">Ini milik kita. Sekarang gali !</font>

42
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,841
<font color="#ffff00">Ham.</font>

43
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,681
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau lakukan ?</font>

44
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,647
<font color="#ffff00">Bunganya bagus.</font>

45
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,445
<font color="#ffff00">Lihat bunga - bunga yang lain ?</font>

46
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,930
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana mereka menempel ke tanah ?</font>

47
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,844
<font color="#ffff00">Di sanalah tempat mereka.</font>

48
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,410
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka punya tujuan.</font>

49
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,481
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka tumbuh.</font>

50
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,323
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu mekar.</font>

51
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:38,250
<font color="#ffff00">Angin membawa benih mereka
lalu tumbuh lebih banyak bunga.</font>

52
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:41,204
<font color="#ffff00">Kita ambil yang akan kita
gunakan dan butuhkan.</font>

53
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,766
<font color="#ffff00">Paham ?</font>

54
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,527
<font color="#ffff00">Shem.</font>

55
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,087
<font color="#ffff00">Ham.</font>

56
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,446
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo.</font>

57
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:23,251
<font color="#ffff00">Ada orang. Sembunyi, sembunyi.</font>

58
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,243
<font color="#ffff00">Cepat.</font>

59
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,324
<font color="#ffff00">Kau temukan buruan kami.</font>

60
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,602
<font color="#ffff00">Sungguh beruntung.</font>

61
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,007
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi tidak bagimu.</font>

62
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:20,408
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tahu berapa lama
kami tak makan daging ?</font>

63
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,850
<font color="#ffff00">Terakhir kali melihat binatang ?</font>

64
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,091
<font color="#ffff00">Tenang.</font>

65
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:44,242
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan. Apa yang kau inginkan ?</font>

66
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,560
<font color="#ffff00">Keadilan.</font>

67
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,560
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa mereka membunuhnya ?</font>

68
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,766
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka memakannya.</font>

69
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,601
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa ?</font>

70
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,443
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka pikir itu membuat
mereka lebih kuat.</font>

71
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,685
<font color="#ffff00">Benarkah ?</font>

72
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:18,210
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka lupa kalau kekuatan
berasal dari Sang Pencipta.</font>

73
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,851
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu !</font>

74
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,526
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu !</font>

75
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,611
<font color="#ffff00">Kau lihat saudara - saudaramu ?</font>

76
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,045
<font color="#ffff00">Ham melihat pemburu.</font>

77
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,202
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka makin dekat.</font>

78
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,720
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana tanggapannya ?</font>

79
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,208
<font color="#ffff00">Sedikit tertarik.</font>

80
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,684
<font color="#ffff00">Dia pasti melihatnya kapan - kapan.</font>

81
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,729
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihat sesuatu yang lain.</font>

82
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,730
<font color="#ffff00">Bunga...</font>

83
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,682
<font color="#ffff00">...yang mekar tiba - tiba.</font>

84
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,881
<font color="#ffff00">Istirahatlah.</font>

85
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:16,281
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin akhirnya Dia akan
memperbaiki keadaan.</font>

86
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,445
<font color="#ffff00">Methuselah.</font>

87
00:11:58,040 --> 00:12:00,646
<font color="#ffff00">Dia bicara kepadamu ?</font>

88
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,245
<font color="#ffff00">Kurasa begitu.</font>

89
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:15,210
<font color="#ffff00">Akankah Dia membantu kita ?</font>

90
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:21,050
<font color="#ffff00">Dia akan menghancurkan dunia.</font>

91
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:29,889
<font color="#ffff00">Ini perjalanan panjang dan
berbahaya bagi anak - anak.</font>

92
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:33,400
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana kau tahu
Kakekmu masih hidup ?</font>

93
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,481
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak tahu.</font>

94
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,720
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihat gunungnya.</font>

95
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:40,088
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus tahu apa dia paham
apa yang harus kita lakukan.</font>

96
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:42,527
<font color="#ffff00">Shem. Bisa bantu aku ?</font>

97
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:50,570
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bisa bawa anak - anak
dan cari persembunyian.</font>

98
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,849
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada kata sembunyi lagi.</font>

99
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:02,651
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus pergi.</font>

100
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,962
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ham, biar Ayah tunjukkan caranya.</i></font>

101
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,080
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dorong sebelah sini.</i></font>

102
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,531
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Saat kita selamat...,</i></font>

103
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,967
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kita akan tahu apa saja
yang kita butuhkan.</i></font>

104
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,568
<font color="#ffff00">Ada kota di depan.</font>

105
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,642
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan terlalu dekat.</font>

106
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:52,043
<font color="#ffff00">Itu tambang tzohar ?</font>

107
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:54,327
<font color="#ffff00">Dulu. Sebelum mereka
menghabiskan semuanya.</font>

108
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,324
<font color="#ffff00">Haruskah kita memutar ?</font>

109
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,961
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

110
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,810
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka semua mati ?</font>

111
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:20,161
<font color="#ffff00">Sepertinya begitu.</font>

112
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,242
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka pasti cuma pemulung.</font>

113
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:24,322
<font color="#ffff00">Dan ada yang merampas dari mereka.</font>

114
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,044
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah !</font>

115
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,523
<font color="#ffff00">Tetaplah berdekatan.</font>

116
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,366
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah !</font>

117
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,521
<font color="#ffff00">Kemari !</font>

118
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,566
<font color="#ffff00">Bisa kulihat ?</font>

119
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,571
<font color="#ffff00">Biar kulihat.</font>

120
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,562
<font color="#ffff00">Katakan siapa namamu.</font>

121
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,250
<font color="#ffff00">Kau punya nama ?</font>

122
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,560
<font color="#ffff00">Ila.</font>

123
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:27,608
<font color="#ffff00">Namaku Ila.</font>

124
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:28,727
<font color="#ffff00">Ila.</font>

125
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,489
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan baik - baik saja, Ila.</font>

126
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:34,604
<font color="#ffff00">Ini Shem.</font>

127
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:38,562
<font color="#ffff00">Dia akan memegang erat
tanganmu dan takkan melepasnya.</font>

128
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:45,006
<font color="#ffff00">Ke atas bukit ! Cepat ! Cepat !</font>

129
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:48,044
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus pergi. Sekarang.</font>

130
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,720
<font color="#ffff00">Ke atas bukit. Lari.</font>

131
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:04,606
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan ke sana.</font>

132
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:10,609
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada pilihan. Cepat !</font>

133
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:29,925
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tahan ! Tahan !</i></font>

134
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,166
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Para raksasa !</i></font>

135
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,921
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mereka akan membunuh kalian !</i></font>

136
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,011
<font color="#ffff00">Shem !</font>

137
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,962
<font color="#ffff00">Jaga Ibumu, selalu.</font>

138
00:16:42,040 --> 00:16:43,280
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah menyayangimu.</font>

139
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,001
<font color="#ffff00">Lari !</font>

140
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,840
<font color="#ffff00">Noah !</font>

141
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,608
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Noah !</i></font>

142
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:20,525
<font color="#ffff00">Noah. Noah. Kau baik - baik saja ?</font>

143
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:53,767
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus bertemu Methuselah.
Kakekku.</font>

144
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,241
<font color="#ffff00">Putra Adam ?</font>

145
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,531
<font color="#ffff00">Kau harusnya membunuh mereka.</font>

146
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:02,166
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi, Samyaza...,</font>

147
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,890
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka manusia, Og.</font>

148
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,844
<font color="#ffff00">Kau lupa bagaimana mereka
mengkhianati Sang Pencipta ?</font>

149
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:09,045
<font color="#ffff00">Dialah yang mengutus kami !</font>

150
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:13,806
<font color="#ffff00">Bohong !</font>

151
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:17,043
<font color="#ffff00">Biarkan mereka membusuk.</font>

152
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,726
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa mereka ?</font>

153
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:37,410
<font color="#ffff00">Watchers.
[Para Penjaga]</font>

154
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,769
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ?</font>

155
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:57,601
<font color="#ffff00">Tidurlah sekarang.</font>

156
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,241
<font color="#ffff00">Bernyanyilah untukku.</font>

157
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:04,088
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingin Ayah menyanyi.</font>

158
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:11,291
<font color="#ffff00">Aku juga kehilangan Ayah
saat masih kecil.</font>

159
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:15,485
<font color="#ffff00">Ada lagu yang dia nyanyikan...</font>

160
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:17,130
<font color="#ffff00">...saat aku tak bisa tidur.</font>

161
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:19,288
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mau mendengarnya ?</font>

162
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,571
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Bulan meninggi.</i></font>

163
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:29,086
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Pepohonan saling membelit.</i></font>

164
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:33,006
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ayahmu menunggumu.</i></font>

165
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:37,810
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Untuk menyelimutimu
dengan sayap pelindung-Nya.</i></font>

166
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:42,121
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan berbisik menyuruhmu tidur.</i></font>

167
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,322
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ayahmu adalah...,</i></font>

168
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:47,727
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Angin penyembuh.</i></font>

169
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:52,522
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Yang berbisik menyuruhmu tidur.</i></font>

170
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:58,004
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Bisikan itu mengantarmu tidur.</i></font>

171
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,644
<font color="#ffff00">Lukanya dalam.</font>

172
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,130
<font color="#ffff00">Dia takkan pernah punya anak.</font>

173
00:20:20,360 --> 00:20:23,887
<font color="#ffff00">Jika demam tak merenggutnya,
Kurasa dia akan hidup.</font>

174
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,371
<font color="#ffff00">Ikuti aku.</font>

175
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:49,407
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf aku menakutimu.</font>

176
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:52,171
<font color="#ffff00">Watchers telah belajar
untuk takut pada manusia.</font>

177
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:54,527
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu kenapa kau membantu kami ?</font>

178
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:01,925
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta menciptakan
kami di hari kedua.</font>

179
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,048
<font color="#ffff00">Hari di saat Dia menciptakan langit.</font>

180
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:07,451
<font color="#ffff00">Kami mengawasi Adam dan Hawa.</font>

181
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:10,404
<font color="#ffff00">Melihat kelemahan dan cinta mereka.</font>

182
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:14,405
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu kami melihat kejatuhan
mereka. Kami kasihan.</font>

183
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:18,923
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Awalnya kami bukan batu,
tapi cahaya.</i></font>

184
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,844
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Sebenarnya kami
tak boleh ikut campur.</i></font>

185
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:25,083
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun kami memilih
membantu umat manusia.</i></font>

186
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,401
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan saat kami tak mematuhi
Sang Pencipta...,</i></font>

187
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:33,969
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dia menghukum kami.</i></font>

188
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:37,601
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kami dilapisi bahan
dari duniamu.</i></font>

189
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:41,127
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Batu dan lumpur membelenggu
cahaya kami.</i></font>

190
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:50,242
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun kami tetap mengajari manusia
semua yang kami tahu soal Penciptaan.</i></font>

191
00:21:51,360 --> 00:21:53,089
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dengan bantuan kami...,</i></font>

192
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:57,564
<font color="#ffff00">...mereka bangkit dari debu,
Jadi hebat dan perkasa.</font>

193
00:21:57,640 --> 00:22:01,770
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi mereka mengubah
karunia kami jadi kekerasan.</font>

194
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:07,327
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Hanya satu orang yang melindungi
kami. Kakekmu Methuselah.</i></font>

195
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:11,846
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kami diburu.
Sebagian besar tewas.</i></font>

196
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:26,285
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Yang masih hidup terpenjara
dengan kulit batu ini...,</i></font>

197
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:29,091
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...terdampar di tanah tandus ini.</i></font>

198
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:32,243
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kami memohon pada Sang Pencipta
untuk membawa kami pulang.</i></font>

199
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:34,681
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tapi Dia selalu diam.</i></font>

200
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:41,524
<font color="#ffff00">Dan sekarang kau bilang kau
mendengar panggilan-Nya.</font>

201
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:43,921
<font color="#ffff00">Samyaza takkan percaya ini.</font>

202
00:22:44,040 --> 00:22:48,364
<font color="#ffff00">Manusia ? Sedangkan manusialah
yang menghancurkan dunia.</font>

203
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,882
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi aku melihatmu...</font>

204
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:55,970
<font color="#ffff00">...dan melihat secercah
cahaya Adam lagi.</font>

205
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:58,042
<font color="#ffff00">Manusia yang kukenal.</font>

206
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:01,686
<font color="#ffff00">Manusia yang ingin kubantu.</font>

207
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:28,209
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa aku tak boleh ikut ?</font>

208
00:23:29,520 --> 00:23:31,727
<font color="#ffff00">Karena Ayah ingin kau jaga Ibu.</font>

209
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:34,486
<font color="#ffff00">Kau paham ?</font>

210
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:44,370
<font color="#ffff00">Jaga Ayahmu.</font>

211
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:53,130
<font color="#ffff00">Jaga mereka.</font>

212
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,248
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka ada di tangan yang benar.</font>

213
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,484
<font color="#ffff00">Kakek ?</font>

214
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,365
<font color="#ffff00">Noah.</font>

215
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:46,006
<font color="#ffff00">Ini Kakek buyutmu.</font>

216
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:48,250
<font color="#ffff00">Beri salam.</font>

217
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,765
<font color="#ffff00">Beritahu namamu.</font>

218
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:55,561
<font color="#ffff00">Aku Shem.</font>

219
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,971
<font color="#ffff00">Putra sulungku.</font>

220
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,811
<font color="#ffff00">Mendekatlah.</font>

221
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:04,842
<font color="#ffff00">Biarkan aku melihatmu.
Kau anak yang beruntung.</font>

222
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:07,645
<font color="#ffff00">Kuyakin kau mirip
dengan Ibumu...,</font>

223
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,404
<font color="#ffff00">...bukan Ayahmu.</font>

224
00:25:10,320 --> 00:25:11,481
<font color="#ffff00">Ceritakanlah tentang dirimu.</font>

225
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:17,969
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang paling kau suka di dunia ?</font>

226
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,086
<font color="#ffff00">Buah Berry.</font>

227
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:22,241
<font color="#ffff00">Apa ?</font>

228
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:23,446
<font color="#ffff00">Berry.</font>

229
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,090
<font color="#ffff00">Berry, ya.</font>

230
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:28,329
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang bisa menandingi Berry
segar dan matang ? Tak ada.</font>

231
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:32,166
<font color="#ffff00">Ya, lama aku tak memakannya
hingga hampir lupa rasanya.</font>

232
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:35,401
<font color="#ffff00">Kau bawa ?</font>

233
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,481
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak ?</font>

234
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:39,402
<font color="#ffff00">Aku menginginkannya sekarang.</font>

235
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:41,482
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin kapan - kapan.</font>

236
00:25:41,560 --> 00:25:43,927
<font color="#ffff00">Kau pasti lelah.
Perjalanan ke sini jauh.</font>

237
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,001
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

238
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:46,485
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa kau tak istirahat ?</font>

239
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:57,408
<font color="#ffff00">Sungguh sempurna.</font>

240
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:02,965
<font color="#ffff00">Yang akan kita diskusikan
bukan untuk anak - anak.</font>

241
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,006
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tahu kenapa aku ke sini ?</font>

242
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:07,286
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

243
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:13,047
<font color="#ffff00">Sebelum pergi, Ayahku Enoch
bilang padaku bahwa suatu hari...,</font>

244
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:16,687
<font color="#ffff00">Jika manusia terus tak berubah...,</font>

245
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:19,286
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta akan
memusnahkan dunia ini.</font>

246
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:20,885
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi yang kulihat benar ?</font>

247
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:24,606
<font color="#ffff00">Semua kehidupan dimusnahkan
karena ulah manusia ?</font>

248
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,324
<font color="#ffff00">Bisakah itu dihindari ?</font>

249
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:32,371
<font color="#ffff00">Noah, percayalah Dia bicara dengan
cara yang bisa kau pahami.</font>

250
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,209
<font color="#ffff00">Katakan.</font>

251
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:36,362
<font color="#ffff00">Bisakah kehancuran ini dihindari ?</font>

252
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:39,881
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

253
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:45,840
<font color="#ffff00">Dia mengutusku ke sini.</font>

254
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:49,851
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa mengutusku jika aku
tak bisa menghentikannya ?</font>

255
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:55,609
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin Dia mengutusmu untuk
minum teh dengan orang tua.</font>

256
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:59,642
<font color="#ffff00">Itukah semua yang kau lihat ?</font>

257
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:02,883
<font color="#ffff00">Api kehancuran dunia ini ?</font>

258
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:06,248
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak, bukan api.</font>

259
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:08,607
<font color="#ffff00">Air.
/ Air ?</font>

260
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:12,328
<font color="#ffff00">Ayahku berkata karena api.</font>

261
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:15,085
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihat air.
Kematian karena air.</font>

262
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,725
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihat kematian.</font>

263
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:21,080
<font color="#ffff00">Dan melihat kehidupan baru.</font>

264
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,968
<font color="#ffff00">Ada hal lain, Kakek.</font>

265
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:29,281
<font color="#ffff00">Hal yang harus kulakukan.
Aku yakin.</font>

266
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,283
<font color="#ffff00">Cuma aku tak tahu apa itu.</font>

267
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,445
<font color="#ffff00">Kehidupan baru.</font>

268
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:39,644
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin masih banyak
yang harus kau lihat.</font>

269
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:43,481
<font color="#ffff00">Apa Dia bukan mengutusmu
untuk minum bersama orang tua ?</font>

270
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:50,289
<font color="#ffff00">Obat rasanya selalu tak enak.</font>

271
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,366
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Hanya dia yang bergerak.</i></font>

272
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,601
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dia terluka parah ?</i></font>

273
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,762
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Luka di perutnya sangat dalam.</i></font>

274
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:58,525
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu dan aku membantu
memegang tangannya.</font>

275
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:01,524
<font color="#ffff00">Pasti itu membuatnya
merasa aman.</font>

276
00:29:01,640 --> 00:29:02,641
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana ?</font>

277
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:05,570
<font color="#ffff00">Api melahap semuanya.</font>

278
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,610
<font color="#ffff00">Air membersihkannya.</font>

279
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:15,564
<font color="#ffff00">Air memisahkan yang busuk dan murni.
Yang jahat dan tak bersalah.</font>

280
00:29:16,120 --> 00:29:19,488
<font color="#ffff00">Itu arti mimpi yang
tenggalam dan naik.</font>

281
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:24,565
<font color="#ffff00">Dia menghancurkan semuanya..,</font>

282
00:29:26,280 --> 00:29:28,886
<font color="#ffff00">...untuk memulai lagi.</font>

283
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:30,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kau yakin ?</font>

284
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:32,731
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

285
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:37,283
<font color="#ffff00">Badai tak bisa dihentikan.
Tapi kita bisa selamat.</font>

286
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:40,401
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

287
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:42,249
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mungkin butuh ini.</font>

288
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:43,810
<font color="#ffff00">Ini benih.</font>

289
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,291
<font color="#ffff00">Dari taman Surga.</font>

290
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,729
<font color="#ffff00">Taman Firdaus.</font>

291
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,004
<font color="#ffff00">Ingat, Noah...,</font>

292
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:54,765
<font color="#ffff00">Dia memilihmu karena suatu alasan.</font>

293
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:04,925
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tak bisa menangkapku !
Kau tak bisa menangkapku !</font>

294
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,690
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah !</font>

295
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:19,529
<font color="#ffff00">Kakekku masih hidup.</font>

296
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:23,282
<font color="#ffff00">Dia membantuku melihat
tujuan kita di sini.</font>

297
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:32,884
<font color="#ffff00">Manusia akan dihukum karena
ulah mereka di dunia ini.</font>

298
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:35,770
<font color="#ffff00">Akan ada kehancuran.</font>

299
00:30:35,840 --> 00:30:38,127
<font color="#ffff00">Akan ada peristiwa sedih.</font>

300
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:43,280
<font color="#ffff00">Dan keluarga kita terpilih
melakukan tugas besar.</font>

301
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:48,122
<font color="#ffff00">Kita terpilih untuk menyelamatkan
yang tak bersalah.</font>

302
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:49,531
<font color="#ffff00">Yang tak bersalah ?</font>

303
00:30:51,120 --> 00:30:52,326
<font color="#ffff00">Para hewan.</font>

304
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:55,165
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa mereka tak bersalah ?</font>

305
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:58,486
<font color="#ffff00">Karena mereka masih hidup
seperti saat di Taman Surga.</font>

306
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:00,801
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

307
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:05,642
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus selamatkan mereka
untuk memulai hidup kembali.</font>

308
00:31:05,760 --> 00:31:07,250
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana dengan kita ?</font>

309
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:18,322
<font color="#ffff00">Kurasa kita harus
memulai hidup baru juga.</font>

310
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:22,603
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bisa mulai di dunia
yang baru dan lebih baik.</font>

311
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,805
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi pertama...,</font>

312
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,450
<font color="#ffff00">...kita harus membangun.</font>

313
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:29,851
<font color="#ffff00">Membangun apa ?</font>

314
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,689
<font color="#ffff00">Banjir besar akan datang.</font>

315
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:41,729
<font color="#ffff00">Air dari langit akan
bertemu air Bumi.</font>

316
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:44,841
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bangun kapal untuk
bertahan dari badai.</font>

317
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:53,362
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bangun sebuah bahtera.</font>

318
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:14,643
<font color="#ffff00">Seret si pengkhianat.</font>

319
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:17,451
<font color="#ffff00">Dia anak Adam !</font>

320
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:19,241
<font color="#ffff00">Berhenti !</font>

321
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:22,811
<font color="#ffff00">Ada tugas yang harus
dikejarkan. Bantu kami.</font>

322
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,848
<font color="#ffff00">Membantu kalian ?</font>

323
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:27,651
<font color="#ffff00">Dulu kami pernah menyelamatkan manusia.</font>

324
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:30,724
<font color="#ffff00">Dan kami kehilangan
segalanya karena kalian !</font>

325
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,401
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak semuanya.</font>

326
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:37,086
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bisa selamatkan yang
tersisa. Melayani-Nya lagi.</font>

327
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:39,848
<font color="#ffff00">Dasar ular berbisa !</font>

328
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:50,409
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta.</font>

329
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:54,929
<font color="#ffff00">Anak - anak !</font>

330
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:03,040
<font color="#ffff00">Apa ini ?</font>

331
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,251
<font color="#ffff00">Ini...,</font>

332
00:34:10,160 --> 00:34:11,924
<font color="#ffff00">Ini bahtera kita.</font>

333
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:26,202
<font color="#ffff00">Kita akan membantu orang ini.</font>

334
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,964
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan !</font>

335
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,686
<font color="#ffff00">Shem.</font>

336
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,011
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu.</font>

337
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:49,167
<font color="#ffff00">Kumohon.</font>

338
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:56,321
<font color="#ffff00">Lukanya masih sakit ?</font>

339
00:37:02,160 --> 00:37:03,685
<font color="#ffff00">Ham !</font>

340
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:05,683
<font color="#ffff00">Shem !</font>

341
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,529
<font color="#ffff00">Dia tak punya siapa - siapa.</font>

342
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,247
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo.</font>

343
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:37,360
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah, kau lihat ?</font>

344
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,771
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ?</font>

345
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,606
<font color="#ffff00">Ya, Japheth.</font>

346
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,005
<font color="#ffff00">Ini sudah dimulai.</font>

347
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:08,360
<font color="#ffff00">Siap ?</font>

348
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,084
<font color="#ffff00">Dia tidur.</font>

349
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:23,285
<font color="#ffff00">Pelan - pelan.</font>

350
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:28,370
<font color="#ffff00">Lihat, yang itu jantan
yang satunya betina.</font>

351
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:31,285
<font color="#ffff00">Setelah badai, mereka
akan jadi Ibu dan Ayah.</font>

352
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:34,250
<font color="#ffff00">Dan anak - anaknya akan
tersebar di seluruh dunia.</font>

353
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,689
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus lembut pada mereka...</font>

354
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,569
<font color="#ffff00">...dan kita harus melindunginya.</font>

355
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:42,641
<font color="#ffff00">Jika terjadi sesuatu...,</font>

356
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:45,246
<font color="#ffff00">...bagian kecil dari Penciptaan
akan hilang selamanya.</font>

357
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:50,084
<font color="#ffff00">Semua makhluk - makhluk
tak berdosa ini dirawat kita.</font>

358
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:54,242
<font color="#ffff00">Tugas kita menjaga mereka.</font>

359
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:09,082
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ?</font>

360
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:10,924
<font color="#ffff00">Semua burung berpasangan.</font>

361
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:15,130
<font color="#ffff00">Kau punya Ibu, Shem punya Ila.</font>

362
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:17,210
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana denganku ?</font>

363
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,126
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana dengan Japheth ?</font>

364
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:22,324
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa pasangan kami ?</font>

365
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:26,363
<font color="#ffff00">Kau lihat bagaimana Dia menciptakan
hutan agar kayunya dijadikan behtera ?</font>

366
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,329
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana Dia mengirim
burung - burung itu ?</font>

367
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:30,846
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi...,</font>

368
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:33,483
<font color="#ffff00">...tidakkah Dia sudah memberi
semua yang kita butuhkan ?</font>

369
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,406
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu !</font>

370
00:41:42,080 --> 00:41:43,491
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa ? Apa ?</font>

371
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:44,971
<font color="#ffff00">Ular !</font>

372
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:54,048
<font color="#ffff00">Ular ikut juga ?
/ Ya.</font>

373
00:41:55,200 --> 00:42:00,001
<font color="#ffff00">Semua hewan merayap,
merangkak dan melata.</font>

374
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,450
<font color="#ffff00">Tenang saja.</font>

375
00:43:21,880 --> 00:43:24,724
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ! Ayah !</font>

376
00:43:26,520 --> 00:43:27,726
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan takut.</font>

377
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:33,561
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan ada yang menyakiti anak ini.</font>

378
00:43:36,440 --> 00:43:37,601
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa namamu ?</font>

379
00:43:39,120 --> 00:43:40,406
<font color="#ffff00">Ham.
/ Ham ?</font>

380
00:43:42,880 --> 00:43:44,723
<font color="#ffff00">Aku Tubal-Cain.</font>

381
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:46,450
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mengenalku ?</font>

382
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:51,124
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tak tahu Rajamu ?</font>

383
00:43:54,160 --> 00:43:58,245
<font color="#ffff00">Ayahku bilang tak ada Raja
di kebun Sang Pencipta.</font>

384
00:44:54,640 --> 00:44:56,847
<font color="#ffff00">Ham, kemarilah.</font>

385
00:45:01,080 --> 00:45:03,321
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan rebut pasukan terbaikku.</font>

386
00:45:04,320 --> 00:45:05,924
<font color="#ffff00">Dia bukan siapa - siapamu.</font>

387
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:09,402
<font color="#ffff00">Lihat senjata di tangannya.
Kurasa dia memegang milikku.</font>

388
00:45:10,320 --> 00:45:11,321
<font color="#ffff00">Ham.</font>

389
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:14,161
<font color="#ffff00">Lepaskan.</font>

390
00:45:14,960 --> 00:45:17,611
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak, dia memberikannya.
/ Turuti ucapan Ayah.</font>

391
00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:34,885
<font color="#ffff00">Saat kudengar tentang mukjizat,
Aku tak mempercayainya.</font>

392
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:39,324
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu kulihat burung - burung
dengan mataku, terbang ke sini...,</font>

393
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,606
<font color="#ffff00">Aku harus datang.</font>

394
00:45:42,400 --> 00:45:43,606
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada sesuatu untukmu di sini.</font>

395
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:45,045
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada ?</font>

396
00:45:45,120 --> 00:45:47,600
<font color="#ffff00">Semua ini milikku.</font>

397
00:45:47,680 --> 00:45:50,081
<font color="#ffff00">Tanah ini. Hutan ini.</font>

398
00:45:51,520 --> 00:45:53,249
<font color="#ffff00">Juga bentengmu.</font>

399
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:57,202
<font color="#ffff00">Kau pikir bisa berlindung
dariku di dalam sana ?</font>

400
00:45:57,320 --> 00:45:59,607
<font color="#ffff00">Itu bukan untuk berlindung darimu.</font>

401
00:45:59,680 --> 00:46:01,045
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu untuk apa ?</font>

402
00:46:01,680 --> 00:46:02,806
<font color="#ffff00">Bahtera...</font>

403
00:46:04,040 --> 00:46:06,042
<font color="#ffff00">...untuk menyelamatkan
yang tak bersalah...</font>

404
00:46:06,160 --> 00:46:08,640
<font color="#ffff00">...saat Sang Pencipta mengirim banjir
untuk melenyapkan orang jahat.</font>

405
00:46:08,720 --> 00:46:10,848
<font color="#ffff00">Sang Pencipta tak peduli
pada dunia ini.</font>

406
00:46:10,920 --> 00:46:14,083
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada kabar dari-Nya sejak Dia
memutuskan hubungan dengan Cain.</font>

407
00:46:14,200 --> 00:46:15,361
<font color="#ffff00">Hanya kami.</font>

408
00:46:15,440 --> 00:46:17,602
<font color="#ffff00">Anak - anak yatim...,</font>

409
00:46:17,720 --> 00:46:22,601
<font color="#ffff00">...dikutuk untuk berjuang dengan
keringat agar bertahan hidup.</font>

410
00:46:22,720 --> 00:46:26,088
<font color="#ffff00">Terkutuk aku jika aku
hanya diam saja.</font>

411
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:28,771
<font color="#ffff00">Terkutuk aku jika tak mengambil
apapun yang kuinginkan.</font>

412
00:46:40,480 --> 00:46:42,050
<font color="#ffff00">Kita pernah bertemu ?</font>

413
00:46:44,280 --> 00:46:45,611
<font color="#ffff00">Aku Putra Lamech !</font>

414
00:46:48,160 --> 00:46:50,367
<font color="#ffff00">Generasi kedelapan dari Seth !</font>

415
00:46:50,440 --> 00:46:52,442
<font color="#ffff00">Kembalilah ke kota kalian,
keturunan Cain !</font>

416
00:46:52,520 --> 00:46:55,729
<font color="#ffff00">Kita semua menghadapi penghakiman !</font>

417
00:46:55,800 --> 00:47:00,124
<font color="#ffff00">Aku punya banyak orang,
Sedang kau sendirian ?</font>

418
00:47:02,160 --> 00:47:03,571
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak sendirian.</font>

419
00:47:14,960 --> 00:47:16,450
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Bawa pergi anak - anak !</i></font>

420
00:47:16,520 --> 00:47:18,170
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan takut, kaumku !</font>

421
00:47:18,280 --> 00:47:20,647
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan takut ! Tegarlah !</font>

422
00:47:20,720 --> 00:47:21,721
<font color="#ffff00">Tahan posisi kalian.</font>

423
00:47:38,240 --> 00:47:40,846
<font color="#ffff00">Kaki tangan-Nya, membelamu ?</font>

424
00:47:44,080 --> 00:47:47,402
<font color="#ffff00">Mukjizat ? Banjir katamu ?</font>

425
00:47:48,520 --> 00:47:50,284
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin kau benar.</font>

426
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:53,926
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin mengusir kita dari
surga tidaklah cukup.</font>

427
00:47:54,000 --> 00:47:58,164
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin, Dia kembali
untuk menghabisi kita.</font>

428
00:47:59,520 --> 00:48:01,443
<font color="#ffff00">Jika memang benar...,</font>

429
00:48:01,520 --> 00:48:04,569
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan melawan badai
menaiki kapalmu.</font>

430
00:48:07,040 --> 00:48:09,281
<font color="#ffff00">Kau dan orang sejenismu
takkan bisa selamat.</font>

431
00:48:12,320 --> 00:48:14,004
<font color="#ffff00">Waktumu sudah habis.</font>

432
00:48:17,720 --> 00:48:19,688
<font color="#ffff00">Tanah ini sekarat.
/ Ham.</font>

433
00:48:19,760 --> 00:48:23,003
<font color="#ffff00">Kota - kota sudah mati.
/ Jangan dengarkan dia.</font>

434
00:48:23,120 --> 00:48:24,884
<font color="#ffff00">Kaumku ikuti aku !</font>

435
00:48:25,640 --> 00:48:27,847
<font color="#ffff00">Yang mau, ikuti mereka !</font>

436
00:48:30,520 --> 00:48:33,603
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak takut pada mukjizat,
Putra Lamech !</font>

437
00:48:33,680 --> 00:48:35,682
<font color="#ffff00">Jika kau menolak lusinan
kaumku sekarang...,</font>

438
00:48:35,800 --> 00:48:38,929
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan kembali dengan pasukan !</font>

439
00:48:51,760 --> 00:48:52,921
<font color="#ffff00">Minggir.</font>

440
00:48:59,120 --> 00:49:00,884
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ?</font>

441
00:49:01,720 --> 00:49:03,563
<font color="#ffff00">Sebenarnya sebanyak
apa yang akan datang ?</font>

442
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:06,803
<font color="#ffff00">Kita selesaikan secepatnya.</font>

443
00:49:06,880 --> 00:49:09,451
<font color="#ffff00">Makin cepat Dia menurunkan
hujan, makin baik.</font>

444
00:49:11,080 --> 00:49:12,730
<font color="#ffff00">Hingga saat itu tiba, kita
lebih aman di dalam.</font>

445
00:49:22,920 --> 00:49:24,285
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bangun.</font>

446
00:49:24,800 --> 00:49:27,121
<font color="#ffff00">Pertama senjata, lalu pasukan.</font>

447
00:49:28,680 --> 00:49:30,887
<font color="#ffff00">Beri makan yang bersedia
bertarung saja.</font>

448
00:49:32,040 --> 00:49:35,044
<font color="#ffff00">Senjatai mereka, latih mereka...,</font>

449
00:49:35,120 --> 00:49:37,691
<font color="#ffff00">...mereka harus bisa segalanya.</font>

450
00:49:38,800 --> 00:49:42,327
<font color="#ffff00">Dengan bala tentara, kita bisa
menghancurkan para raksasa itu.</font>

451
00:51:13,040 --> 00:51:15,042
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kumohon, kami lapar !</i></font>

452
00:51:15,120 --> 00:51:16,770
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Beri kami daging.
/ Anak - anak kami kelaparan.</i></font>

453
00:51:16,840 --> 00:51:18,080
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tolong kami !</i></font>

454
00:51:21,520 --> 00:51:22,965
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Lepaskan kami !</i></font>

455
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:25,004
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kami kelaparan !</i></font>

456
00:51:58,960 --> 00:52:00,450
<font color="#ffff00">Haruskah aku kembali ?</font>

457
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:02,845
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

458
00:52:03,920 --> 00:52:06,082
<font color="#ffff00">Menurutmu mereka
akan menyerang kita ?</font>

459
00:52:08,400 --> 00:52:09,765
<font color="#ffff00">Saat hujan turun.</font>

460
00:52:15,840 --> 00:52:17,410
<font color="#ffff00">Menurutmu akan seperti apa ?</font>

461
00:52:22,040 --> 00:52:24,008
<font color="#ffff00">Aku sudah melihatnya.</font>

462
00:52:25,040 --> 00:52:27,122
<font color="#ffff00">Melihat banyak kematian...,</font>

463
00:52:29,680 --> 00:52:32,684
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak tahu cara menggambarkannya.</font>

464
00:52:35,080 --> 00:52:36,491
<font color="#ffff00">Akhir dari segalanya.</font>

465
00:52:39,960 --> 00:52:43,282
<font color="#ffff00">Awal.
Awal dari segalanya.</font>

466
00:52:49,600 --> 00:52:50,761
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa ?</font>

467
00:52:52,280 --> 00:52:54,521
<font color="#ffff00">Apapun yang terjadi,
Shem sangat mencintaimu.</font>

468
00:53:02,520 --> 00:53:04,522
<font color="#ffff00">Shem butuh seorang wanita.</font>

469
00:53:07,520 --> 00:53:09,124
<font color="#ffff00">Wanita yang sesungguhnya.</font>

470
00:53:11,040 --> 00:53:12,690
<font color="#ffff00">Dia harus punya keluarga.</font>

471
00:53:14,160 --> 00:53:15,685
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak bisa memberi
keturunan padanya.</font>

472
00:53:19,120 --> 00:53:22,090
<font color="#ffff00">Aku takkan menyangkal itu...,</font>

473
00:53:22,160 --> 00:53:23,650
<font color="#ffff00">...meski dia menginginkannya.</font>

474
00:53:24,400 --> 00:53:26,243
<font color="#ffff00">Aku takkan melakukannya.</font>

475
00:53:26,320 --> 00:53:27,481
<font color="#ffff00">Selain itu...,</font>

476
00:53:27,560 --> 00:53:31,007
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa Sang Pencipta ingin
gadis mandul di bahtera-Nya ?</font>

477
00:53:31,880 --> 00:53:33,450
<font color="#ffff00">Ila. Ila.</font>

478
00:53:35,480 --> 00:53:37,323
<font color="#ffff00">Saat pertama kami membawamu...,</font>

479
00:53:38,640 --> 00:53:40,847
<font color="#ffff00">Kupikir kau akan jadi beban.</font>

480
00:53:41,680 --> 00:53:45,207
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak ingin melihat orang lain
jadi buruk sebab dunia ini.</font>

481
00:53:46,400 --> 00:53:48,050
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi aku salah.</font>

482
00:53:49,080 --> 00:53:50,206
<font color="#ffff00">Kau anugerah.</font>

483
00:53:50,360 --> 00:53:52,283
<font color="#ffff00">Anugerah yang sangat berharga.</font>

484
00:53:52,880 --> 00:53:55,565
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan lupa betapa
berharganya dirimu.</font>

485
00:54:09,680 --> 00:54:13,287
<font color="#ffff00">Kau pasti akan mencari istri
untuk Ham dan Japheth.</font>

486
00:54:15,800 --> 00:54:18,246
<font color="#ffff00">Carikan untuk Shem juga.
/ Ila.</font>

487
00:55:00,600 --> 00:55:02,011
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kau mau lari mana ?</i></font>

488
00:55:05,920 --> 00:55:07,445
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kumohon, jangan bawa anakku !</i></font>

489
00:55:08,080 --> 00:55:10,367
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Lepaskan ! Kumohon !</i></font>

490
00:55:10,440 --> 00:55:12,329
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf, kami harus makan !</font>

491
00:55:12,400 --> 00:55:14,926
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan bawa anakku ! Jangan !</font>

492
00:55:15,040 --> 00:55:18,567
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan bawa anakku !
Tolong hentikan dia.</font>

493
00:55:18,640 --> 00:55:20,404
<font color="#ffff00">Lepaskan mereka !</font>

494
00:55:25,120 --> 00:55:27,441
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak !</font>

495
00:55:31,600 --> 00:55:33,443
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan melawan !
Agar lebih mudah.</font>

496
00:55:34,200 --> 00:55:36,248
<font color="#ffff00">Ikut aku ! Jangan melawan !</font>

497
00:55:38,200 --> 00:55:40,328
<font color="#ffff00">Kau ! Kau !</font>

498
00:55:55,680 --> 00:55:59,446
<font color="#ffff00">Aku punya dua gadis !
Dua gadis untuk ditukar !</font>

499
00:56:00,720 --> 00:56:02,449
<font color="#ffff00">Ambil gadis - gadisnya !
Beri aku daging !</font>

500
00:56:02,600 --> 00:56:03,647
<font color="#ffff00">Berikan padaku !</font>

501
00:57:43,000 --> 00:57:44,001
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang terjadi ?</font>

502
00:57:46,840 --> 00:57:49,366
<font color="#ffff00">Semuanya harus dimasukkan sekarang.</font>

503
00:57:49,480 --> 00:57:50,527
<font color="#ffff00">Badai akan datang.</font>

504
00:57:50,600 --> 00:57:51,840
<font color="#ffff00">Istri kami ? Di mana ?</font>

505
00:57:51,920 --> 00:57:53,160
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tak dengar Ayah ?</font>

506
00:57:53,240 --> 00:57:54,321
<font color="#ffff00">Kapan mereka datang ?</font>

507
00:57:56,080 --> 00:57:57,286
<font color="#ffff00">Takkan ada istri.</font>

508
00:57:58,240 --> 00:57:59,844
<font color="#ffff00">Apa ? Apa ? Tidak !</font>

509
00:57:59,920 --> 00:58:02,048
<font color="#ffff00">Kau bilang Sang Pencipta akan
memberi yang kita butuhkan.</font>

510
00:58:02,120 --> 00:58:04,122
<font color="#ffff00">Bantulah Kakakmu.
/ Tidak.</font>

511
00:58:04,280 --> 00:58:05,964
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah tak bisa melakukan ini !</font>

512
00:58:06,040 --> 00:58:07,929
<font color="#ffff00">Tak bisa. Bagaimana aku
bisa jadi pria dewasa ?</font>

513
00:58:08,080 --> 00:58:09,286
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah bilang bantu Kakakmu.</font>

514
00:58:10,560 --> 00:58:12,130
<font color="#ffff00">Kau ingin aku tetap
jadi anak - anak !</font>

515
00:58:12,200 --> 00:58:13,725
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak !</font>

516
00:58:15,720 --> 00:58:20,726
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah ingin kau dewasa
dan tunaikan tugasmu.</font>

517
00:58:28,640 --> 00:58:29,801
<font color="#ffff00">Ham !</font>

518
00:58:33,120 --> 00:58:34,281
<font color="#ffff00">Ham !</font>

519
00:58:55,360 --> 00:58:56,930
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau lakukan, Noah ?</font>

520
00:58:57,400 --> 00:58:59,368
<font color="#ffff00">Kejahatan tak hanya
ada pada mereka.</font>

521
00:59:00,320 --> 00:59:01,890
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi dalam diri kita semua.</font>

522
00:59:03,240 --> 00:59:04,526
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihatnya.</font>

523
00:59:07,680 --> 00:59:08,681
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

524
00:59:09,040 --> 00:59:10,121
<font color="#ffff00">Noah.</font>

525
00:59:11,160 --> 00:59:12,844
<font color="#ffff00">Ada kebaikan dalam diri kita.</font>

526
00:59:13,840 --> 00:59:15,604
<font color="#ffff00">Lihat anak - anak kita.</font>

527
00:59:15,680 --> 00:59:18,524
<font color="#ffff00">Kesetiaan Shem. Kebaikan Japheth.</font>

528
00:59:19,320 --> 00:59:21,800
<font color="#ffff00">Keteguhan Ham.</font>

529
00:59:23,440 --> 00:59:24,646
<font color="#ffff00">Anak - anak baik.</font>

530
00:59:25,440 --> 00:59:27,363
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka akan jadi
Ayah yang baik.</font>

531
00:59:27,720 --> 00:59:29,609
<font color="#ffff00">Shem dibutakan keinginan.</font>

532
00:59:30,840 --> 00:59:32,604
<font color="#ffff00">Ham suka iri hati.</font>

533
00:59:33,720 --> 00:59:35,927
<font color="#ffff00">Dan Japheth hidupnya cuma
untuk senang - senang.</font>

534
00:59:36,200 --> 00:59:37,201
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak lebih baik.</font>

535
00:59:37,320 --> 00:59:38,970
<font color="#ffff00">Dan kau ?</font>

536
00:59:40,200 --> 00:59:44,285
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan lakukan apapun demi
tiga putramu, baik atau buruk, kan ?</font>

537
00:59:44,360 --> 00:59:48,285
<font color="#ffff00">Kita berdua akan membunuh
demi melindungi anak kita.</font>

538
00:59:48,360 --> 00:59:49,521
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

539
00:59:50,880 --> 00:59:52,211
<font color="#ffff00">Kita sama saja.</font>

540
00:59:54,040 --> 00:59:56,964
<font color="#ffff00">Kita lemah dan egois, merasa
posisi kita akan nyaman.</font>

541
00:59:58,640 --> 01:00:02,406
<font color="#ffff00">Kita akan bekerja,
menyelesaikan tugas...,</font>

542
01:00:03,720 --> 01:00:05,051
<font color="#ffff00">...lalu kita akan mati.</font>

543
01:00:06,960 --> 01:00:09,122
<font color="#ffff00">Sama seperti yang lain.</font>

544
01:00:10,640 --> 01:00:12,051
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka masih anak - anak !</font>

545
01:00:12,200 --> 01:00:14,407
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka anak kita, Noah !</font>

546
01:00:16,560 --> 01:00:18,005
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kau tak punya belas kasih ?</font>

547
01:00:20,200 --> 01:00:22,202
<font color="#ffff00">Waktu untuk mengasihi telah berlalu.</font>

548
01:00:24,480 --> 01:00:26,403
<font color="#ffff00">Sekarang hukuman
kita telah dimulai.</font>

549
01:00:57,920 --> 01:00:59,365
<font color="#ffff00">Ham !</font>

550
01:01:03,800 --> 01:01:04,801
<font color="#ffff00">Ham !</font>

551
01:01:17,920 --> 01:01:19,365
<font color="#ffff00">Kakek ?</font>

552
01:01:25,960 --> 01:01:27,450
<font color="#ffff00">Kakek ?</font>

553
01:01:30,320 --> 01:01:31,810
<font color="#ffff00">Kau membawa sesuatu ?</font>

554
01:01:34,440 --> 01:01:36,807
<font color="#ffff00">Noah menanam benih yang kuberi ?</font>

555
01:01:37,800 --> 01:01:38,801
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

556
01:01:40,280 --> 01:01:43,204
<font color="#ffff00">Dan di hutan itu tak ada
Berry sama sekali ?</font>

557
01:01:43,960 --> 01:01:45,962
<font color="#ffff00">Shem menjanjikan Berry padaku.</font>

558
01:01:49,160 --> 01:01:50,321
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

559
01:01:50,440 --> 01:01:51,441
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak tahu.</font>

560
01:01:53,000 --> 01:01:54,286
<font color="#ffff00">Sayang sekali.</font>

561
01:01:57,320 --> 01:01:58,890
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu kenapa kau kemari ?</font>

562
01:02:02,760 --> 01:02:04,171
<font color="#ffff00">Noah.</font>

563
01:02:04,280 --> 01:02:06,726
<font color="#ffff00">Dia melarang putra kami berpasangan.</font>

564
01:02:06,840 --> 01:02:08,922
<font color="#ffff00">Shem punya Ila, tapi dia mandul.</font>

